{"tid":2372704,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"手提電腦不停自動開機熄機係咪冇得救？","createTime":"2021-01-20T01:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T11:52:53.000Z","uid":4341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d410670937f9f1e6304a28945a80610c8d7bb6db","tid":2372704,"uid":4341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T01:58:50.000Z","msg":"開機時不停閃閃下，之後又自動熄一熄機再自動開返機無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開始閃閃下以為個mon 壞，用hdmi 去左電視睇都係咁結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我google 睇好似係個底版壞，咁係咪冇救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整仲貴過買？<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下因為壞得太突然冇back up，買新notebook時，可唔可以拆舊個hard drive 出黎入返去新電腦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟咩都唔識，跪求各位高人指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf0947d0e59bd83b822bd11bf8acc885acf0963","tid":2372704,"uid":4341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:14:13.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9126b66a1a1a71dca7242b0a69e39b26e995bc5b","tid":2372704,"uid":269681,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"去搵定神父好啲 似有啲野<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20d71fbee17cc8b059e926a711e41069272c4dc","tid":2372704,"uid":366977,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"有得整，聽落似燒左chips或者燒電容<br />\n去代理問下先<br />\n部機時間都耐嘅話買過新仲好<br />\nHardrive未必可以重用，有d電腦得m.2接口<br />\n通常平價機或者打機電腦先會有mSATA<br />\n同埋一拆機就會冇左保養<br />\n不如搵部電腦抄d資料出黎，跟住換部新機"},{"pid":"a765fe7ad97f5991b3fe4879a90db57eebf9553c","tid":2372704,"uid":75164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T00:40:13.000Z","msg":"boot loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc3189b62bf6d29d87fa017895f8cfcf347862f","tid":2372704,"uid":194922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:36:16.000Z","msg":"過左保未，過左就拆後蓋清主板d塵，重上散熱膏睇下有無用"},{"pid":"bd332dc1762382d5a856cabc8f7071b13a96625c","tid":2372704,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"Cpu個散熱裝得太實都有呢個情況<br />\n直情好似無電到 一係不停reboot"}]}